@host = http://localhost:5080
@token = 0123456789ABCDEFFEDCBA9876543210

### Health
GET {{host}}/health

### Decide: minimum available balance probe
POST {{host}}/v1/subscription-credit/decide
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "requestedCredits": "1",
  "creditAmountMode": "minimum-available-balance",
  "extraPoolAuthorization": "not-authorized",
  "idempotencyKey": "manual-run-001",
  "correlationId": "corr-manual-run-001-admission",
  "source": "manual-http"
}

### Consume: actual usage settlement
POST {{host}}/v1/subscription-credit/consume
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "requestedCredits": "120",
  "creditAmountMode": "exact-credits",
  "extraPoolAuthorization": "not-authorized",
  "idempotencyKey": "manual-run-001",
  "correlationId": "corr-manual-run-001-settlement",
  "source": "manual-http"
}

### Invalid token format: lowercase credential should fail
POST {{host}}/v1/subscription-credit/decide
Authorization: Bearer 0123456789abcdeffedcba9876543210
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "requestedCredits": "1",
  "creditAmountMode": "minimum-available-balance",
  "extraPoolAuthorization": "not-authorized",
  "idempotencyKey": "manual-invalid-token",
  "correlationId": "corr-manual-invalid-token",
  "source": "manual-http"
}
